## Module boundaries (encapsulation)

Decompose tasks along **module boundaries** so concurrent scopes don't overlap. If your project already declares boundaries in `.claude/rules/*.md`, reference them here rather than duplicating.

| Module / area | Path(s) | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `<module-a>` | `<path/to/a/**>` | |
| `<module-b>` | `<path/to/b/**>` | |

