## Notes

- **Shared state hazards** (not file-scoped): `VERSION`, lockfiles (`package-lock.json`, `poetry.lock`), `triggers.json`, migration sequence files. Two sessions bumping these race even in separate worktrees → `/deploy` guards `VERSION` with `git fetch && git diff origin/<branch>`. Coordinate other shared files via a claim row covering them.
- **Platform:** `git worktree` needs git ≥ 2.5; verify on Git Bash/Windows before relying on `auto` (see `CLAUDE.local.md ## Branching`).
- This file is **project-owned** — sync adds it if missing but never overwrites your claims.
